{
  "stem": "11671.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we all marched about two or three miles to the outskirts of the city, which was a, a brick factory.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's where we were gathered to be taken to camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we stayed in this brick factory for about-- oh, about two weeks and waited for transport to be taken to work camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, we were, we were terribly crowded.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And every family received just, like, a corner, so we were, like, in a room about this size, an average room size, maybe 12 by 12, and we each-- a family had to, to lie down and make room, you know, just for about eight or 10 people in this small area.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we children-- we were four children and my mother and father, and we just got a corner in this little factory.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we stayed there, and we, we tried to make the best of it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We sang songs, and we, we flirted with the boys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were all, you know, young girls, 15, 17.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my brother was 19, my sister 21.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we just sang songs and, and prayed and, and played games and tried to make the best of it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we couldn't wait to be taken already so that-- because we thought, now, nothing can be worse than this, you know, to live on a floor in such temporary headquarters so--",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had taken food from home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we did not get any food from outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had taken food from home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People brought food, and some of the outsiders-- I don't know who they were, but they brought some additional food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in this, in this brick factory about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, we were lined up and taken to trains.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
